{"tid":2310030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家可唔可以follow多啲海外香港人page","createTime":"2020-12-03T03:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T06:32:02.000Z","uid":234894,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"38a3d1113a53e5de6582c596be7d33877be6f699","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"其實唔知大家有冇留意過，一直以來每當有海外香港人組織搞活動，通常媒體都只會一句「海外港人組織」帶過，令到好多海外手足佢哋嘅關注度嚴重不足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rA7sGEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrA7sGEo.jpg&h=d87d88e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/nfahkatjapan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnfahkatjapan&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=fbf8afb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/nfahkatjapan</a><br />\n例如之前入過日本國會嘅「香港建國聯盟」佢哋Twitter竟然剩係得280Follow<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5wk1Ev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5wk1Ev.jpg&h=31b0f98b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fb.me/wethehongkongers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.me%2Fwethehongkongers&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d6ddf48b\" target=\"_blank\">www.fb.me/wethehongkongers</a><br />\n喺美國嗰邊呼籲大家人口普查填「HongKonger」，亦都有積極參加各種嘅聲援活動嘅「We The HongKonger」Facebook竟然剩係得7000幾個Like<br />\n<br />\n其實一直以來呢一班海外嘅手足都有不斷努力打好國際線，如果大家可以幫幫手就去留意多啲佢哋嘅資訊。更何況大家都知香港嘅情況，未來國際線將會係一條非常重要嘅戰線，多啲留意國際線嘅動向，知道喺外國仲有咁多手足做緊嘢，點都係一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n介紹幾個海外組織俾各位巴打<br />\n波士頓香港人權組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKSAMBOS/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKSAMBOS%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=b17c1118\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKSAMBOS/</a><br />\n<br />\n思政學陣 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/VHKPoActs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FVHKPoActs%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6503ef97\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/VHKPoActs/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳港聯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/auhklink\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fauhklink&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=c363fee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/auhklink</a><br />\nStand with HK at JPN<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/StandwithHKJPN/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStandwithHKJPN%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=8427122d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/StandwithHKJPN/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港思源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104009074829573/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104009074829573%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=706632e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104009074829573/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果要睇比較論述向小小嘅，可以睇吓呢兩本<br />\n<br />\n新香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sanhoenggong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsanhoenggong&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=b6793e09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sanhoenggong</a><br />\nIG:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thenewhongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthenewhongkong%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6dcee140\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/thenewhongkong/</a><br />\n<br />\n自由港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/harbouroffreedom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fharbouroffreedom%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=77c934c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/harbouroffreedom/</a><br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HarbourofFreedomHongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHarbourofFreedomHongKong&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d5938162\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HarbourofFreedomHongKong</a>"},{"pid":"7432e8fc6d7c1c5dd7116c1372eedffebed6d8b1","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8836cf627c80966b71a49bfa409b0d1bbfdcabc2","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39f8cdd0bc5c502c66dcf6a4960803c5a5c002f","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2184c992fac81d45d073572af1a936fe02f1b4ec","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1a1f2b8a857314b6b783bd12c05aa05d72fea9","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6191dec352cfac9c564c47e62ec9c1b97c0ead14","tid":2310030,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T03:34:15.000Z","msg":